room_title: Escape room "Th3 C0d3" by Escapology Rockwall in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: The Code reviewGame was awesome got held up on last clue punching in ck #'s loved it will do it again. I live in Jersey was visiting family in Texas they did it before and couldn't wait for me to get there so we could all do it together. Staff is very friendly and pleasant too. Really nice place!

room_title: Escape room "Th3 C0d3" by Escapology Rockwall in Dallas-Fort Worth
review: We ( 3 adults and 2 kids) had a great time doing th3 c0d3 escape room. Blaise was our game master and explained everything very well to us since this was our first time trying an escape room. We got out with just under seven minutes remaining, the stress was real (fun).
